    "body": "### Problem\n\nThere is a fair amount of boilerplate required to implement an Ex command via Lua. \n\nExample: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/843a7223e77d63be496e6bcfbe1fca89b7010266/src/nvim/ex_docmd.c#L8295\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nFind a way to reduce the boilerplate, via build-time generators and/or a C macro.",
